Package: oplpctools
Version: #version#-1
Section: games
Architecture: #arch#
Priority: extra
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.15), libqt5widgets5 (>= 5.6.0), libqt5gui5 (>= 5.6.0)
Maintainer: Sergey Smolyannikov <brainstream@yandex.ru>
Description: Tools for managing PS2 disk images used in Open PlayStation 2 Loader
 Abilities:
     - Create OPL games from ISO files
     - Create OPL games from CD/DVD discs
     - Assign pictures for games (such as cover and icon)
